{"tid":2047374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"同袍制服沒編號 警：分唔到邊個","createTime":"2020-06-02T05:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T05:25:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b7f34436bae3b3c3226d7e3ed196b438e323de3","tid":2047374,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:14:40.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200602/2ZL5KLA7I2FHG46YANYLTYOE6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2F2ZL5KLA7I2FHG46YANYLTYOE6U%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=b57603e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2F2ZL5KLA7I2FHG46YANYLTYOE6U%2F&h=05fdf969\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200602/2ZL5KLA7I2FHG46YANYLTYOE6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n同袍制服沒編號 警：分唔到邊個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WQWU5G6AGIFFGTFWIOMHETIFYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWQWU5G6AGIFFGTFWIOMHETIFYM.jpg&h=5e60ada1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&lt;br /&gt;被告杜依蘭及湯偉雄昨到區域法院續審。 &lt;br /&gt;黃耀興攝&lt;br /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n【「赴湯杜火」案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年7.28上環警民衝突，湯氏夫婦與一名少女被控參與暴動，湯被指舉高雙手阻擋警員追截，讓身後兩名正攀越鐵絲網的女子逃脫。案件昨續審，於當天追截三人的警員供稱，湯被捕時表現合作，他不能斷言湯是為了阻撓警員而舉高雙手，不排除是同袍要求湯這樣做。他亦同意其隊員身穿的制服沒有警察編號，自己也「分唔到邊個打邊個」。<br />\n<br />\n湯。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n嚴。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不確定被告舉手為阻撓警員<br />\n<br />\n嚴。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC872/19<br />\n■記者廖希呈"},{"pid":"ffd85cf4a394e693733d249873d3db910e1483c6","tid":2047374,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b7f34436bae3b3c3226d7e3ed196b438e323de3","tid":2047374,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:14:40.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/l